data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Tracing collects a detailed profile of all operations occurring inside CRM Server. This data is helpful in conversations with support. Enabling tracing has a large performance impact. Use it only for specific problems that are occurring. Do not enable tracing for a long time.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Microsoft CRM Server configuration relies on many different areas like Registry, AD, IIS or SQL Db for instance. To create a file that contains information about the CRM Server and its environment, click on 'Generate' button.
